dialog.body: Hello! Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Daniel Bennett. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Maria. Could you please provide me with the license plate number of your vehicle?
Sure, it's Alpha Bravo Charlie one two three four.
Thank you. Can you also confirm the last four digits of your social security number for verification purposes?
Of course, it's five six seven eight.
Great, thank you for providing that information, Maria. Is there anything specific you need assistance with today?
I need to check the status of a claim I filed last week.
I can help with that. Thank you for your time, Maria. Let me look into that for you.
Thank you for your patience, Maria. Your claim is currently under review. We will reach out to you with updates as soon as possible.
Thank you for contacting us, Maria. Have a great day!
